hasAttributes.name: parentId
hasAttributes.description: Choose the customer's address.

hasAttributes.name: parentIdTypeCode
hasAttributes.description: The name of the entity linked by parentId

hasAttributes.name: customerAddressId
hasAttributes.description: Unique identifier of the customer address.

hasAttributes.name: addressNumber
hasAttributes.description: Shows the number of the address, to indicate whether the address is the primary, secondary, or other address for the customer.

hasAttributes.name: objectTypeCode
hasAttributes.description: Shows the type code of the customer record to indicate whether the address belongs to a customer account or contact.

hasAttributes.name: addressTypeCode
hasAttributes.description: Select the address type, such as primary or billing.

hasAttributes.name: name
hasAttributes.description: Type a descriptive name for the customer's address, such as Corporate Headquarters.

hasAttributes.name: primaryContactName
hasAttributes.description: Type the name of the primary contact person for the customer's address.

hasAttributes.name: line1
hasAttributes.description: Type the first line of the customer's address to help identify the location.

hasAttributes.name: line2
hasAttributes.description: Type the second line of the customer's address.

hasAttributes.name: line3
hasAttributes.description: Type the third line of the customer's address.

hasAttributes.name: city
hasAttributes.description: Type the city for the customer's address to help identify the location.

hasAttributes.name: stateOrProvince
hasAttributes.description: Type the state or province of the customer's address.

hasAttributes.name: county
hasAttributes.description: Type the county for the customer's address.

hasAttributes.name: country
hasAttributes.description: Type the country or region for the customer's address.

hasAttributes.name: postOfficeBox
hasAttributes.description: Type the post office box number of the customer's address.

hasAttributes.name: postalCode
hasAttributes.description: Type the ZIP Code or postal code for the address.

hasAttributes.name: UTCOffset
hasAttributes.description: Select the time zone for the address.

hasAttributes.name: freightTermsCode
hasAttributes.description: Select the freight terms to make sure shipping charges are processed correctly.

hasAttributes.name: UPSZone
hasAttributes.description: Type the UPS zone of the customer's address to make sure shipping charges are calculated correctly and deliveries are made promptly, if shipped by UPS.

hasAttributes.name: latitude
hasAttributes.description: Type the latitude value for the customer's address, for use in mapping and other applications.

hasAttributes.name: telephone1
hasAttributes.description: Type the primary phone number for the customer's address.

hasAttributes.name: longitude
hasAttributes.description: Type the longitude value for the customer's address, for use in mapping and other applications.

hasAttributes.name: shippingMethodCode
hasAttributes.description: Select a shipping method for deliveries sent to this address.

hasAttributes.name: telephone2
hasAttributes.description: Type a second phone number for the customer's address.

hasAttributes.name: telephone3
hasAttributes.description: Type a third phone number for the customer's address.

hasAttributes.name: fax
hasAttributes.description: Type the fax number associated with the customer's address.

hasAttributes.name: versionNumber
hasAttributes.description: Version number of the customer address.

hasAttributes.name: createdBy
hasAttributes.description: Shows who created the record.

hasAttributes.name: createdOn
hasAttributes.description: Shows the date and time when the record was created. The date and time are displayed in the time zone selected in Microsoft Dynamics 365 options.

hasAttributes.name: modifiedBy
hasAttributes.description: Shows who last updated the record.

hasAttributes.name: modifiedOn
hasAttributes.description: Shows the date and time when the record was last updated. The date and time are displayed in the time zone selected in Microsoft Dynamics 365 options.

hasAttributes.name: owningBusinessUnit
hasAttributes.description: Shows the business unit that the record owner belongs to.

hasAttributes.name: owningUser
hasAttributes.description: Unique identifier of the user who owns the customer address.

hasAttributes.name: timeZoneRuleVersionNumber
hasAttributes.description: For internal use only.

hasAttributes.name: overriddenCreatedOn
hasAttributes.description: Date and time that the record was migrated.

hasAttributes.name: UTCConversionTimeZoneCode
hasAttributes.description: Time zone code that was in use when the record was created.

hasAttributes.name: importSequenceNumber
hasAttributes.description: Unique identifier of the data import or data migration that created this record.

hasAttributes.name: ownerId
hasAttributes.description: Owner Id

hasAttributes.name: ownerIdType
hasAttributes.description: The type of owner, either User or Team.

hasAttributes.name: createdOnBehalfBy
hasAttributes.description: Shows who created the record on behalf of another user.

hasAttributes.name: modifiedOnBehalfBy
hasAttributes.description: Shows who last updated the record on behalf of another user.

hasAttributes.name: transactionCurrencyId
hasAttributes.description: Choose the local currency for the record to make sure budgets are reported in the correct currency.

hasAttributes.name: exchangeRate
hasAttributes.description: Shows the conversion rate of the record's currency. The exchange rate is used to convert all money fields in the record from the local currency to the system's default currency.

hasAttributes.name: composite
hasAttributes.description: Shows the complete address.

definitions.description: Address and shipping information. Used to store additional addresses for an account or contact.
